_json.title: 8 Ways to Make an Extra $1000 a Month On a Small Homestead
_json.gridTitle: 8 Ways to Make an Extra $1000 a Month On a Small Homestead
_json.description: We’ve all seen them. Those huge lists with ideas for making money on your homestead. A laundry list of things that could potentially bring in income, but mostly just a few dollars here or there. But what about real income? I’m talking income that actually pays the bills and helps you live the life you want without taking up a lot of time. How can you meaningfully contribute to your home economy while still living the life you love?

creator.name: Practical Self Reliance - Preserving Food & Homestead Survival
